`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
The caustic plane reuses `buildWaterPlaneGeometry` (same footprint), positioned at `y - CAUSTICS_DEPTH_OFFSET`. `THREE.AdditiveBlending` adds `src_alpha * src_rgb` to the destination — the bright caustic rings appear to "light up" whatever's below without occlusion, which matches the "light projection" visual semantics. `depthWrite: false` prevents the transparent plane from blocking scene objects.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`

